WEBVTT

01:05.000 --> 01:06.460
Did it sound like Wen Lang?

01:11.000 --> 01:12.530
I practiced for a long time.

01:15.590 --> 01:17.120
What I played for you

01:19.560 --> 01:20.690
was the best played.

01:30.350 --> 01:31.230
Did you like it?

02:52.180 --> 02:57.810
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:58.180 --> 03:00.580
[Episode 24]

03:07.030 --> 03:08.690
Who's that person next to him?

03:13.310 --> 03:14.110
What's wrong?

03:14.560 --> 03:16.290
Let's watch it again together.

03:23.000 --> 03:24.400
Get Zhou Chuan over here.

03:24.960 --> 03:25.430
Coming.

03:25.430 --> 03:26.430
Go, go.

03:28.400 --> 03:29.460
It's an interview?

03:30.190 --> 03:30.920
It's a video.

03:31.000 --> 03:31.930
Oh, it's a video.

03:32.310 --> 03:33.579
He and Zhao Ping should be friends.

03:33.579 --> 03:34.960
The former Deputy Captain
of the Cheetah Strike Force.

03:34.960 --> 03:36.150
In social situations,

03:36.150 --> 03:38.030
you can judge how intimate two people are

03:38.030 --> 03:39.660
based on their distance.

03:40.310 --> 03:42.030
This is often referred to in psychology as

03:42.030 --> 03:43.490
interpersonal distance.

03:44.030 --> 03:45.370
The most handsome guy of our unit,

03:45.370 --> 03:46.840
Captain Zhou Chuan!

03:46.870 --> 03:47.240
Applause!

03:47.240 --> 03:48.630
The distance between us right now

03:48.630 --> 03:50.490
shows an intimate relationship.

03:50.990 --> 03:51.840
Further away

03:52.360 --> 03:53.430
would be the distance

03:53.430 --> 03:55.490
between acquaintances and friends.

03:55.870 --> 03:56.800
But look,

03:57.690 --> 04:00.750
their distance is so short
throughout the whole video.

04:01.310 --> 04:02.640
Zhao Ping is his friend,

04:03.280 --> 04:05.400
but he looks very resistant to him.

04:06.150 --> 04:06.960
You are right.

04:08.430 --> 04:09.800
They are physically very close,

04:09.800 --> 04:10.730
but their bodies

04:10.750 --> 04:12.150
are in a defensive state.

04:12.670 --> 04:13.590
His left toe is

04:13.720 --> 04:15.190
pointing in the opposite direction,

04:15.190 --> 04:16.850
looking for a chance to leave.

04:17.019 --> 04:18.120
They get along with each other,

04:18.120 --> 04:19.560
but there is a barrier between them,

04:19.560 --> 04:20.620
or even conflicts.

04:22.050 --> 04:23.450
If we can find this person

04:23.750 --> 04:24.190
and ask about

04:24.190 --> 04:26.450
what happened in the SWAT team back then,

04:26.600 --> 04:28.070
maybe we can get new clues

04:28.190 --> 04:29.270
about the 8/17 Case

04:29.430 --> 04:31.890
and your brother from another perspective.

04:41.040 --> 04:41.900
Do you know him?

04:45.480 --> 04:47.070
I can't see his face clearly.

04:47.070 --> 04:48.130
This is too blurry.

04:48.830 --> 04:50.040
I need to reconfirm.

04:53.800 --> 04:55.460
I'm hungry, Professor Jiang.

04:56.630 --> 04:59.230
Which cafeteria in your college
has good food?

05:01.390 --> 05:02.790
I have to ask my students.

05:03.000 --> 05:03.920
Go ahead.

05:04.360 --> 05:05.040
Just right,

05:05.350 --> 05:06.480
I need the restroom.

05:11.720 --> 05:13.580
It's on the left when you head out.

05:36.630 --> 05:37.240
Wei.

05:37.940 --> 05:38.560
Hello.

05:38.810 --> 05:39.540
I'm Zhan Wei.

05:39.830 --> 05:40.560
Jin.

05:41.370 --> 05:43.830
You should take
a good look at your marriage.

05:44.480 --> 05:47.070
Is Jiang Hansheng with you
because he loves you,

05:47.070 --> 05:48.730
or does he have other motives?

05:48.950 --> 05:50.950
Will your former SWAT colleagues go

05:51.120 --> 05:53.040
to Nephew's one-month party?

05:54.070 --> 05:55.720
They are all busy people now.

05:56.000 --> 05:57.270
They might not come.

05:57.720 --> 05:58.430
Why?

05:59.560 --> 06:01.620
Did Brother have any enemies before?

06:02.240 --> 06:03.900
How could he have any enemies?

06:04.240 --> 06:06.170
Why would you suddenly think that?

06:19.480 --> 06:20.740
There is a charity fund

06:21.160 --> 06:22.360
under He Wu's name.

06:24.240 --> 06:25.070
There were

06:25.750 --> 06:28.720
two anonymous donations
of over a million within a year.

06:28.720 --> 06:29.390
They end up

06:29.720 --> 06:31.270
on his own account,

06:32.110 --> 06:33.909
leaving the source untracable.

06:35.950 --> 06:37.990
Do you want to know Qi's background?

06:39.690 --> 06:40.610
Did he give in?

06:41.240 --> 06:42.070
Not yet.

06:42.840 --> 06:44.700
He's waiting for the sentencing.

06:45.040 --> 06:46.390
The courtyard you found

06:46.920 --> 06:48.870
was found by his former lover.

06:49.270 --> 06:50.630
They are from the same hometown—

06:50.630 --> 06:52.950
both from Xiagai Village, Jishui.

06:53.360 --> 06:54.040
Qi's

06:54.500 --> 06:56.300
original name is Guo Zhengying.

06:56.480 --> 06:58.430
His mother died when he was young.

06:59.000 --> 07:01.210
His father
couldn't pay off his usury loans,

07:01.210 --> 07:03.830
so he was beaten to death
by the debt collectors.

07:03.830 --> 07:05.450
Guo Zhengying stabbed two people to death

07:05.450 --> 07:06.710
using a butcher knife.

07:06.950 --> 07:08.310
He then fled to the mountains

07:08.310 --> 07:09.770
and was found a week later.

07:10.160 --> 07:11.980
After being released from prison,

07:11.980 --> 07:13.110
he left his hometown

07:13.260 --> 07:15.320
and went to Jingzhou to make a living.

07:17.040 --> 07:17.720
That's it?

07:18.120 --> 07:20.180
We are still investigating the rest.

07:25.140 --> 07:25.760
By the way,

07:26.270 --> 07:28.640
two employees of Hengyun Logistics Company

07:28.640 --> 07:29.940
have confessed

07:30.830 --> 07:32.290
to a child abduction case.

07:32.750 --> 07:34.270
Those from the Anti-Human Trafficking Department
came this morning.

07:34.270 --> 07:35.510
It is currently confirmed

07:35.510 --> 07:36.600
that the child is 3 years old,

07:36.600 --> 07:38.930
and the parents have been looking for her.

07:41.040 --> 07:42.570
I've seen that little girl.

07:43.270 --> 07:44.600
She can finally go home.

07:45.480 --> 07:46.210
That's good.

07:48.600 --> 07:49.510
I can see

07:49.980 --> 07:51.860
you still care about your work.

07:54.510 --> 07:55.800
Of course I do.

07:56.510 --> 07:58.220
It's just that what I can do,

07:58.240 --> 07:59.760
anyone else can do.

07:59.790 --> 08:03.030
And it's more convenient for them to do so
given my identity.

08:03.030 --> 08:05.230
I don't have any special value anymore.

08:05.560 --> 08:07.830
Rather than wandering around your team
and causing people annoyance,

08:07.830 --> 08:09.430
it's better for me
to have some self-awareness.

08:09.430 --> 08:11.070
Causing who annoyance?

08:14.360 --> 08:14.870
Come in.

08:18.280 --> 08:20.370
Are you... feeling better?

08:21.920 --> 08:22.750
I'm fine.

08:23.220 --> 08:23.950
What is it?

08:24.240 --> 08:24.920
Mentor,

08:24.940 --> 08:27.140
there's an urgent situation
I need to report to you.

08:27.140 --> 08:27.610
Sure.

08:27.950 --> 08:28.630
Director Wang

08:28.630 --> 08:30.640
recently came into contact
with the latest witness

08:30.640 --> 08:32.070
in the Huaiguang serial murder cases.

08:32.070 --> 08:32.950
These new clues

08:32.980 --> 08:35.440
are directly related
to Qi Yan's background.

08:35.440 --> 08:37.080
So I want to go to Jingzhou

08:37.360 --> 08:38.620
to look into this clue.

08:38.789 --> 08:40.480
It might give us a new direction.

08:40.480 --> 08:41.030
You can,

08:41.270 --> 08:43.120
but you can't go alone.

08:43.280 --> 08:44.940
I'll find someone to help you.

08:47.720 --> 08:49.520
Professor Jiang will go with me.

08:49.940 --> 08:50.780
Your husband?

08:52.270 --> 08:53.440
Does he have time?

08:53.440 --> 08:55.200
This isn't something that can be solved
in a day or two.

08:55.200 --> 08:56.730
He applied for a secondment

08:56.910 --> 08:58.040
to focus on the case.

08:58.100 --> 08:58.960
That works too.

08:59.270 --> 09:02.330
After all, Professor Jiang
is familiar with Jingzhou.

09:02.360 --> 09:04.820
Besides,
he's in charge of this case anyway.

09:06.510 --> 09:07.370
How about this?

09:07.550 --> 09:09.690
Wan and the others are there too, right?

09:09.690 --> 09:10.600
Once you arrive,

09:10.600 --> 09:12.130
contact them immediately.

09:12.360 --> 09:13.200
It's best...

09:14.790 --> 09:16.030
Don't worry.

09:16.480 --> 09:18.090
Let's wait for the superior's arrangements

09:18.090 --> 09:19.570
for your future work.

09:19.600 --> 09:22.120
How can they arrange for anything
if I can't even be reinstated?

09:22.120 --> 09:23.320
They'll probably a police station

09:23.320 --> 09:24.780
and assign me a cushy spot—

09:24.870 --> 09:28.000
somewhere I can stay comfortably
for the rest of my life.

09:34.790 --> 09:36.120
What are you looking at?

09:37.720 --> 09:38.650
Get back to work!

09:52.070 --> 09:53.600
What are you yelling about?

09:54.910 --> 09:56.440
What are you yelling about?

09:58.270 --> 10:01.270
If you have anything on your mind,
just tell me nicely.

10:12.040 --> 10:13.440
I have nothing on my mind.

10:14.050 --> 10:16.510
I'll obey the organization's arrangement.

10:20.260 --> 10:21.690
H-Have a good rest.

10:22.510 --> 10:24.370
Report to me anytime if anything.

10:31.510 --> 10:32.200
It's over.

10:32.640 --> 10:34.500
He has completely lost his faith.

10:39.030 --> 10:39.600
Mentor,

10:40.060 --> 10:41.090
can you help him?

10:41.550 --> 10:42.670
How do I help him?

10:43.150 --> 10:44.120
I can fight for

10:44.320 --> 10:45.720
his honor as a policeman.

10:46.080 --> 10:47.540
But as for his love trauma—

10:48.030 --> 10:49.890
is that something I can help with?

10:51.250 --> 10:51.970
Of course.

10:52.600 --> 10:53.400
You can't help

10:53.890 --> 10:55.490
at this point of time either.

10:57.360 --> 10:58.360
Life's

10:58.550 --> 10:59.550
twists and turns—

11:00.620 --> 11:02.350
he can only face them on his own.

11:05.510 --> 11:07.150
Can he have his lighter back now?

11:07.150 --> 11:07.750
Oh, right.

11:07.830 --> 11:10.630
I would have forgotten
if you hadn't mentioned it.

11:13.000 --> 11:13.600
Here.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.270
I have some things to say to him.

11:16.270 --> 11:16.910
Okay.

11:18.190 --> 11:19.880
Don't agitate him too much!

11:25.590 --> 11:26.320
Jiang Cheng.

11:30.150 --> 11:30.950
Wait a minute.

11:31.750 --> 11:32.550
Don't come in.

11:32.750 --> 11:33.910
I smell like smoke all over.

11:33.910 --> 11:35.000
You can't stand it.

11:36.240 --> 11:37.120
So you know.

11:37.550 --> 11:39.080
Then smoke less from now on.

11:39.110 --> 11:40.440
It would be best to quit.

11:43.870 --> 11:45.330
Is it any of your business?

11:46.620 --> 11:47.580
No, it's not.

11:55.630 --> 11:56.830
Why did you follow me?

11:57.870 --> 11:59.390
I just called Bin.

12:00.080 --> 12:02.240
I asked him to come
to keep you company for a couple of days

12:02.240 --> 12:03.480
and have him keep an eye on you.

12:03.480 --> 12:04.080
What's your problem?

12:04.080 --> 12:06.280
Why do I need someone
to keep an eye on me?

12:08.360 --> 12:09.270
I wanted him to bring you

12:09.270 --> 12:11.870
your favorite
preserved mustard greens buns.

12:14.070 --> 12:15.350
Fine, fine.

12:22.150 --> 12:23.750
I haven't touched the money

12:23.960 --> 12:25.820
you deposited in your debit card.

12:26.550 --> 12:28.880
The PIN has been changed to your birthday.

12:29.510 --> 12:30.910
That money is for you.

12:31.320 --> 12:32.200
I can't use it.

12:38.120 --> 12:40.650
If you won't use it,
just donate it somewhere.

12:43.390 --> 12:45.520
Is Jiang Hansheng's family very rich?

12:47.980 --> 12:49.190
If I said that I married him

12:49.190 --> 12:50.760
for his money,

12:51.360 --> 12:52.630
would you feel better?

12:53.630 --> 12:55.230
Then I would look down on you.

12:58.220 --> 12:59.200
How is he?

12:59.600 --> 13:01.240
I heard that to stop your car,

13:01.240 --> 13:03.040
he almost fell off the mountain.

13:03.500 --> 13:05.060
He usually looks ordinary,

13:05.190 --> 13:06.590
but in critical moments,

13:06.630 --> 13:07.360
he's not bad.

13:07.450 --> 13:09.780
This is the first time you've praised him.

13:10.000 --> 13:11.580
Jiang Hansheng is not ordinary.

13:11.580 --> 13:13.500
He used to work in the Provincial Bureau.

13:13.500 --> 13:14.380
Tsk.

13:14.870 --> 13:16.600
I don't want to hear about this.

13:39.150 --> 13:39.910
Jin,

13:40.230 --> 13:41.560
are you playing with me?

13:54.750 --> 13:55.720
Cheng.

14:01.360 --> 14:02.120
Zhou Jin,

14:03.080 --> 14:03.870
you keep following me around—

14:03.870 --> 14:05.870
what exactly do you want to say to me?

14:08.480 --> 14:09.840
I just want to say,

14:14.020 --> 14:15.440
whether I exist or not,

14:17.480 --> 14:19.410
you are still the same Jiang Cheng.

14:20.270 --> 14:21.670
It's because you are good

14:22.440 --> 14:23.720
that I liked you.

14:24.320 --> 14:26.080
It's because you are confident,

14:26.080 --> 14:26.840
brave,

14:27.270 --> 14:28.480
and shining,

14:29.550 --> 14:31.120
that I liked you

14:31.320 --> 14:32.550
for many years.

14:33.750 --> 14:35.950
Regardless of whether I like you or not,

14:36.440 --> 14:38.030
you are the best person,

14:38.150 --> 14:39.360
the best policeman.

15:12.700 --> 15:15.350
Have Bin give the debit card back to me.

15:17.080 --> 15:19.010
I'll treat him to a feast for 3 days.

15:24.550 --> 15:26.150
I miss Jin!

16:09.150 --> 16:09.870
Who is it?

16:09.890 --> 16:11.350
Hello, you have a package.

16:15.780 --> 16:16.270
Hello.

16:16.270 --> 16:17.200
Are you Mr. Wang?

16:17.480 --> 16:18.270
This is your parcel.

16:18.270 --> 16:18.930
Take a look.

16:21.450 --> 16:22.880
[Hello, Prof Wang.
This is a gift to Professor Jiang.]

16:27.960 --> 16:28.670
Prof.

16:29.320 --> 16:31.550
Zhou Jin and I
are going to Jingzhou tonight.

16:31.550 --> 16:33.010
Are you free this evening?

16:59.000 --> 17:00.400
I have some new speculations

17:00.400 --> 17:01.630
regarding Qi Yan, her brother,

17:01.630 --> 17:02.840
and her father

17:03.080 --> 17:05.210
I'd like to talk to you in person about.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.270
Sorry,

17:55.350 --> 17:58.080
the number you dialed
is currently unavailable.

18:09.680 --> 18:10.440
Prof?

18:14.920 --> 18:16.520
I'm the security guard here.

18:16.750 --> 18:18.640
I saw you kept calling, so I answered.

18:18.640 --> 18:19.200
Well...

18:19.200 --> 18:20.480
Something happened to Professor Wang.

18:20.480 --> 18:22.610
An ambulance took him to the hospital.

18:25.640 --> 18:26.310
Hansheng,

18:26.400 --> 18:27.000
what's wrong?

18:27.000 --> 18:28.600
Something happened to Prof.

18:28.920 --> 18:29.790
What happened?

18:30.000 --> 18:30.930
He was attacked.

18:31.240 --> 18:32.040
It's serious.

18:32.110 --> 18:33.000
Who did it?

18:33.000 --> 18:33.730
I don't know.

18:33.920 --> 18:34.830
It could be Qi Yan

18:34.830 --> 18:35.790
or a previous criminal.

18:35.790 --> 18:36.680
Anything is possible.

18:36.680 --> 18:37.480
Hansheng,

18:37.550 --> 18:38.400
don't panic.

18:38.440 --> 18:39.310
Wait for me at home.

18:39.310 --> 18:40.200
I'll be right back to pick you up.

18:40.200 --> 18:41.200
We'll go to Jingzhou.

18:41.200 --> 18:41.790
Okay.

18:41.810 --> 18:43.070
Don't scare yourself.

18:43.440 --> 18:44.100
Wait for me.

18:54.680 --> 18:55.510
Mr. Wan.

18:55.880 --> 18:57.070
Something happened to Mr. Wang.

18:57.070 --> 18:58.530
Can you go to the Crime Research Lab

18:58.530 --> 19:00.640
to help me
find out the specific situation?

19:00.640 --> 19:01.790
Something happened to Director Wang?

19:01.790 --> 19:03.440
It is said that he was attacked.

19:03.440 --> 19:04.830
Okay, I'll ask around.

19:04.960 --> 19:06.960
Okay, I'll be waiting for your news.

19:15.670 --> 19:16.350
Hansheng.

19:16.590 --> 19:17.750
Did you bring your ID card?

19:17.750 --> 19:18.350
Yes.

19:19.920 --> 19:20.450
Let's go.

19:20.450 --> 19:21.250
Get in the car.

19:33.500 --> 19:34.410
[Mr. Wan]

19:35.830 --> 19:36.680
Mr. Wan,

19:36.720 --> 19:37.550
hold on.

19:38.590 --> 19:39.590
I got the details.

19:40.000 --> 19:40.750
The attacker

19:40.750 --> 19:42.790
is a criminal Director Wang
helped catch before.

19:42.790 --> 19:43.700
He just got out of prison.

19:43.700 --> 19:45.590
This time he disguised himself
as a courier

19:45.590 --> 19:46.900
and attacked Director Wang with a hammer.

19:46.900 --> 19:48.350
Fortunately,
the security guard arrived quickly,

19:48.350 --> 19:49.640
so the attacker didn't escape.

19:49.640 --> 19:51.040
How is Director Wang now?

19:51.200 --> 19:52.000
Not very good.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.350
He suffered severe head trauma.

19:53.350 --> 19:54.960
Although he was sent
to the hospital in time,

19:54.960 --> 19:56.590
he is still in the operating room.

19:56.590 --> 19:57.500
Has the suspect been interrogated?

19:57.500 --> 19:58.160
After the man was caught,

19:58.160 --> 19:59.240
he confessed quickly,

19:59.240 --> 20:00.350
saying that
after he was released from prison,

20:00.350 --> 20:01.550
he couldn't reintegrate into society,

20:01.550 --> 20:03.240
so he wanted
to take revenge on Director Wang.

20:03.240 --> 20:04.720
Captain Qian and I
are going to go take a look.

20:04.720 --> 20:06.440
The police have searched his home.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.510
They found nothing.

20:07.510 --> 20:09.240
But at his parents' house,

20:09.240 --> 20:11.040
they found 100,000 yuan in cash.

20:11.110 --> 20:12.510
According to his parents,

20:12.510 --> 20:13.390
this 100,000 yuan

20:13.390 --> 20:15.110
was left for them by their son
for their retirement.

20:15.110 --> 20:16.960
He couldn't reintegrate into society
but had so much money?

20:16.960 --> 20:17.880
So,

20:17.880 --> 20:21.340
we can't rule out the possibility
that he was hired by someone.

20:21.400 --> 20:23.070
Someone is already following up on it.

20:23.070 --> 20:24.200
You wait for my news.

20:24.230 --> 20:25.550
I'll go to the police station first,

20:25.550 --> 20:27.010
and then go to the hospital
to see Director Wang.

20:27.010 --> 20:27.700
Okay.

20:27.730 --> 20:28.750
Thank you, Mr. Wan.

20:28.750 --> 20:29.960
You're the most welcome.

20:29.960 --> 20:31.240
Be safe on the road.

20:32.920 --> 20:33.550
Zhu,

20:33.550 --> 20:34.680
how much longer are we?

20:34.680 --> 20:35.550
About half an hour.

20:35.550 --> 20:36.070
Don't worry,

20:36.070 --> 20:37.930
I'll try to be as fast as possible.

20:40.480 --> 20:41.510
It must be Qi Yan.

20:42.400 --> 20:43.510
I can't be wrong.

20:49.550 --> 20:50.510
Don't worry.

20:50.750 --> 20:51.960
Mr. Wang will be fine.

20:52.460 --> 20:54.390
I didn't expect him to attack Prof.

20:55.400 --> 20:56.640
It's my negligence.

20:57.340 --> 20:57.970
Hansheng,

20:58.440 --> 20:59.400
don't worry.

20:59.440 --> 21:00.970
Let's see when we get there.

21:16.590 --> 21:17.480
How is Prof?

21:21.070 --> 21:21.790
-Jiang Hansheng!
-What are you doing?

21:21.790 --> 21:23.750
Jiang Hansheng,
how do you have the nerve to come here?

21:23.750 --> 21:24.770
Hubby, let go first.

21:24.770 --> 21:25.750
Let go!

21:26.200 --> 21:26.770
Are you okay?

21:26.770 --> 21:27.500
Calm down.

21:27.590 --> 21:28.680
Dad is still in there.

21:28.680 --> 21:29.440
Calm down?

21:29.830 --> 21:30.510
How can I?

21:31.370 --> 21:33.070
The old man was already retired,

21:33.070 --> 21:34.760
but he went back to work
because of him.

21:34.760 --> 21:35.690
Jiang Hansheng.

21:36.920 --> 21:38.030
You should know better than me

21:38.030 --> 21:39.360
why he's lying in there.

21:39.720 --> 21:41.050
When my mom passed away,

21:41.510 --> 21:43.200
what did you promise her?

21:44.070 --> 21:45.400
I'm telling you, Jiang Hansheng.

21:45.400 --> 21:47.060
If anything happens to my dad,

21:48.200 --> 21:48.920
you'll pay!

21:49.160 --> 21:49.960
I'm sorry.

21:50.640 --> 21:51.070
I'm sorry.

21:51.070 --> 21:52.470
Apologizing is useless!

21:52.510 --> 21:54.840
He is the one lying in there today,
not you!

21:55.200 --> 21:56.110
What are you yelling about?

21:56.110 --> 21:57.350
This is a hospital.

21:57.480 --> 21:58.680
Please be quiet!

21:59.920 --> 22:01.110
Hubby, calm down.

22:02.520 --> 22:03.920
I'm going out for a smoke.

22:07.400 --> 22:08.270
I'm sorry.

22:08.990 --> 22:11.450
My husband is just too worried
about his dad,

22:11.500 --> 22:12.780
so he spoke out of turn.

22:13.880 --> 22:14.960
We actually know

22:15.770 --> 22:17.500
this has nothing to do with you.

22:21.640 --> 22:22.440
Hansheng.

22:23.070 --> 22:24.400
It's good that you came.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.640
He'll be very happy to see you

22:26.640 --> 22:27.750
when he wakes up.

22:31.720 --> 22:32.400
Thank you.

22:33.680 --> 22:34.550
How is

22:35.590 --> 22:36.680
Mr. Wang doing now?

22:39.640 --> 22:40.480
I don't know.

22:42.110 --> 22:43.370
He hasn't woken up yet.

22:45.510 --> 22:46.560
It'd be a hard blow

22:47.550 --> 22:49.750
for someone his age to be hit by a hammer.

22:53.750 --> 22:54.550
You guys take a seat first.

22:54.550 --> 22:56.080
I'll go check on my husband.

23:39.480 --> 23:41.210
Do you want to sleep for a while?

23:44.160 --> 23:45.020
I'm not sleepy.

23:47.920 --> 23:48.780
Are you hungry?

23:49.920 --> 23:51.520
Do you want something to eat?

23:52.830 --> 23:53.790
I can buy you

23:54.680 --> 23:56.160
some wontons

23:56.960 --> 23:57.960
and beef noodles.

23:59.160 --> 23:59.820
How's that?

24:06.000 --> 24:07.800
Last time I went to Prof's house,

24:09.110 --> 24:10.970
he cooked a bowl of noodles for me.

24:13.270 --> 24:14.840
He was perfectly fine then.

24:22.880 --> 24:23.920
He'll be fine.

24:26.310 --> 24:27.920
Mr. Wang will recover.

24:44.240 --> 24:44.830
Zhou Jin.

24:49.390 --> 24:51.390
I think I did something wrong again.

24:53.550 --> 24:54.270
No.

24:55.440 --> 24:57.100
You didn't do anything wrong.

24:57.160 --> 24:57.920
Really.

25:00.680 --> 25:02.280
It has nothing to do with you.

25:05.070 --> 25:06.270
It's not your fault.

25:39.510 --> 25:40.770
My dad wants to see you.

25:43.590 --> 25:44.080
Go ahead.

25:44.080 --> 25:45.340
I'll wait for you here.

26:22.830 --> 26:23.550
Prof.

26:29.240 --> 26:29.890
Prof.

26:42.290 --> 26:43.570
Pup.

26:45.200 --> 26:46.440
Don't cry.

26:51.610 --> 26:52.920
Don't be impulsive.

26:55.410 --> 26:57.710
Think about Zhou.

27:01.200 --> 27:03.350
The guy who hit me

27:04.960 --> 27:06.960
said he was delivering a gift

27:07.770 --> 27:10.090
to me for someone else.

27:14.720 --> 27:16.590
There's a mastermind behind this.

27:16.590 --> 27:17.920
Do you know who?

27:20.790 --> 27:21.880
It's Qi Yan.

27:23.160 --> 27:24.680
He

27:27.160 --> 27:28.810
wants to take revenge on you.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.640
Be careful.

27:34.960 --> 27:36.400
Be careful.

27:49.270 --> 27:50.170
Hansheng.

27:53.000 --> 27:53.920
Hansheng.

27:56.480 --> 27:58.550
My good student,

28:00.500 --> 28:02.390
my good friend.

28:04.000 --> 28:06.590
I know what you're thinking.

28:12.480 --> 28:14.680
Don't let hatred

28:16.110 --> 28:18.200
blind you.

28:22.160 --> 28:23.030
Professor.

28:25.240 --> 28:26.720
It's my fault.

28:28.110 --> 28:29.790
You were dragged into this.

28:32.590 --> 28:35.110
It is your fault.

28:37.830 --> 28:39.030
So

28:41.310 --> 28:44.790
you have to take care of me in my old age
and see me off.

29:07.750 --> 29:09.070
I'm tired.

29:10.920 --> 29:12.780
I can't keep my eyes open anymore.

30:24.480 --> 30:26.200
Officer Jiang.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.120
Do you feel it?

30:30.920 --> 30:32.830
You can't save anyone.

30:37.590 --> 30:38.440
Don't touch her!

30:38.440 --> 30:40.040
Death is actually not scary.

30:41.350 --> 30:43.640
Death is the true beginning

30:45.650 --> 30:47.170
It brings new life.

31:22.730 --> 31:23.490
Hansheng.

31:24.350 --> 31:25.110
How is he?

31:26.440 --> 31:27.200
It's fine.

31:27.720 --> 31:28.720
He'll get better.

31:29.830 --> 31:31.560
I'm going to go see the attacker

31:31.610 --> 31:33.140
and ask him a few questions.

31:33.350 --> 31:35.270
I'll have Mentor
contact the police station.

31:35.270 --> 31:35.830
No need.

31:37.250 --> 31:38.700
Jingzhou is my home turf.

31:43.160 --> 31:44.440
I picked it up.

31:44.850 --> 31:46.450
How many times have I said it?

31:46.550 --> 31:48.210
100,000 is not a small amount.

31:49.960 --> 31:51.730
Did you give this sum to your parents?

31:51.730 --> 31:53.410
No, I spent it.

31:54.030 --> 31:56.000
I bought alcohol and cigarettes.

31:56.160 --> 31:57.200
I bought food too.

31:57.200 --> 31:58.070
Stop talking nonsense.

31:58.070 --> 31:59.420
100,000 is not a small amount.

31:59.420 --> 32:00.750
Can it be spent that fast?

32:00.750 --> 32:02.830
How would I know? I'm a fast spender.

32:03.280 --> 32:05.290
I open 10 bottles of alcohol at a time.

32:05.290 --> 32:06.030
Makes sense, right?

32:06.030 --> 32:06.240
And after that

32:06.240 --> 32:09.200
I went to eat barbecue with the guys.

32:09.220 --> 32:10.790
I also have to...

32:10.820 --> 32:12.170
Well...

32:12.510 --> 32:14.110
Stop messing around with me.

32:15.070 --> 32:16.550
Who's messing around?

32:16.550 --> 32:18.340
I'm talking to you seriously.

32:20.390 --> 32:22.240
I just don't know.

32:22.270 --> 32:23.720
I don't care what you say.

32:24.510 --> 32:26.350
Sentence me if you want, okay?

32:28.080 --> 32:29.410
Are you guys done or not?

32:30.350 --> 32:31.310
Hurry up!

32:31.720 --> 32:33.310
If you can't get an answer, stop asking!

32:33.310 --> 32:35.240
I'm telling you, I just don't know!

32:35.920 --> 32:38.120
Why don't you get someone else to ask me?

32:38.160 --> 32:39.030
Hansheng.

32:40.880 --> 32:41.750
I'll do it.

33:01.160 --> 33:02.290
Someone new to interrogate me?

33:02.290 --> 33:02.770
Okay.

33:02.880 --> 33:03.920
You ask.

33:03.920 --> 33:04.750
Go on.

33:05.270 --> 33:05.920
Shi Qiang.

33:06.770 --> 33:08.230
I'll ask you one last time.

33:08.350 --> 33:10.240
Where did this 100,000 yuan come from?

33:10.240 --> 33:11.400
I don't know.

33:13.070 --> 33:14.160
I picked it up.

33:15.030 --> 33:16.600
I forgot when I picked it up.

33:16.710 --> 33:18.040
Where did you pick it up?

33:19.250 --> 33:20.450
Where did I pick it up?

33:22.150 --> 33:22.840
I forgot.

33:28.680 --> 33:29.830
You guys draft

33:30.270 --> 33:31.600
what questions you ask?

33:34.640 --> 33:35.370
Keep asking.

33:38.450 --> 33:39.170
Go ahead.

33:46.780 --> 33:47.980
What's going on here?

33:48.990 --> 33:49.830
You got someone new,
but they're not saying anything?

33:49.830 --> 33:51.360
What's the meaning of this?

33:52.400 --> 33:53.610
If you're not going to ask,
get someone new.

33:53.610 --> 33:54.540
Get someone new.

33:54.790 --> 33:56.920
Get someone who speaks.

34:07.700 --> 34:08.710
Someone new?

34:08.840 --> 34:09.440
Okay.

34:10.060 --> 34:10.870
Hurry.

34:11.560 --> 34:12.170
Come on.

34:16.510 --> 34:17.070
Let's go.

34:20.880 --> 34:22.400
Speak!

34:22.400 --> 34:24.130
Why aren't you talking either?

34:25.280 --> 34:26.610
Are you playing with me?

34:27.440 --> 34:28.770
Are you playing with me?

34:34.840 --> 34:36.239
If you don't talk, I will.

34:37.190 --> 34:38.670
Name: Shi Qiang.

34:38.760 --> 34:39.840
Age: 32.

34:39.920 --> 34:40.800
Gender: Male.

34:41.159 --> 34:42.380
Where did the 100,000 yuan come from?

34:42.380 --> 34:43.110
I don't know.

34:43.120 --> 34:45.040
I picked it up. Where did you pick it up?

34:45.040 --> 34:45.690
I forgot.

34:48.190 --> 34:49.210
Any other questions? Ask away.

34:49.210 --> 34:50.670
Come on, change the topic.

34:53.110 --> 34:54.190
Ask!

35:02.300 --> 35:03.480
You're back, officer.

35:03.480 --> 35:04.440
Come.

35:04.460 --> 35:05.670
Is it time to eat?

35:05.700 --> 35:06.940
Shouldn't we eat?

35:06.960 --> 35:09.890
Officers, I've been starving for 5 hours.

35:10.020 --> 35:10.870
Are you guys

35:10.890 --> 35:13.750
interrogating me
like this without giving me food?

35:14.340 --> 35:16.180
Right. Open it.

35:16.850 --> 35:18.510
How does it taste? Is it sweet?

35:18.510 --> 35:19.460
I need to eat something sweet now.

35:19.460 --> 35:21.660
I'm low on blood sugar, I'm telling you.

35:23.990 --> 35:25.150
Give me a piece.

35:27.940 --> 35:29.470
Don't just eat it yourself!

35:29.960 --> 35:31.520
Give me a piece!

35:32.310 --> 35:33.670
It's been 5 hours!

35:34.760 --> 35:36.590
Are you just ignoring me?

35:38.350 --> 35:39.680
Can I have a sip of water?

35:40.660 --> 35:41.990
Can I have a sip of water?

35:42.070 --> 35:45.190
My throat is dry. It's smoking.

36:14.400 --> 36:15.150
I know you.

36:16.630 --> 36:17.440
Mr. Jiang.

36:17.440 --> 36:18.500
I'm talking to you.

36:19.920 --> 36:20.800
I know you.

36:30.450 --> 36:32.380
How do you know my surname is Jiang?

36:33.130 --> 36:34.060
You're talking.

36:34.440 --> 36:35.370
You're talking!

36:36.100 --> 36:38.030
It's none of your business how I know you.

36:38.030 --> 36:38.760
I also know that old man

36:38.760 --> 36:40.220
is your teacher, isn't he?

36:40.670 --> 36:43.000
That's why they say
old people are useless.

36:43.000 --> 36:44.710
I just hit him with a hammer...

36:47.700 --> 36:48.960
And he was done for.

36:49.070 --> 36:51.130
Blood splattered all over the floor.

36:51.530 --> 36:52.930
Too bad you didn't see it.

36:54.400 --> 36:57.260
The person who hired you
told you to say that, right?

37:02.920 --> 37:04.930
Let me think what else he taught you.

37:16.240 --> 37:17.280
He also told you

37:19.070 --> 37:20.600
that after you were caught,

37:21.320 --> 37:22.360
you'd meet a man

37:23.400 --> 37:24.660
named Jiang Hansheng,

37:25.190 --> 37:26.840
a student of Wang Pengze.

37:27.950 --> 37:29.680
But you don't need to be afraid.

37:30.510 --> 37:32.750
You just need to provoke him
using his teacher,

37:32.750 --> 37:34.460
and he'll be led by the nose.

37:35.210 --> 37:37.140
The more exaggerated, the better.

37:39.590 --> 37:41.520
Given this person's personality,

37:41.630 --> 37:43.230
he would also mock me.

37:45.030 --> 37:45.890
He would say...

37:47.840 --> 37:50.480
Jiang Hansheng is a pretentious person.

37:50.960 --> 37:52.420
He claims to be righteous,

37:52.920 --> 37:54.920
but he's actually easy to deal with.

38:01.110 --> 38:02.640
Looks like I guessed right.

38:06.060 --> 38:07.150
What a pity.

38:08.030 --> 38:09.360
Five years have passed,

38:09.630 --> 38:11.290
and he hasn't improved at all.

38:12.400 --> 38:13.400
But Shi Qiang,

38:14.230 --> 38:16.880
do you know why
he only dares to hire a murderer?

38:18.440 --> 38:19.290
Why?

38:22.180 --> 38:24.710
Because he doesn't dare
to fight me directly.

38:25.080 --> 38:27.020
Something even he doesn't dare to do—

38:27.020 --> 38:27.950
how would you?

38:29.400 --> 38:29.880
Honestly speaking,

38:29.880 --> 38:31.280
I'm not interested in

38:31.280 --> 38:33.340
in where your 100,000 yuan came from.

38:33.600 --> 38:35.600
But as for what you did to my teacher,

38:36.650 --> 38:38.850
that's a score I have to settle with you.

38:40.670 --> 38:41.930
How will you settle it?

38:45.440 --> 38:46.440
What do you mean?

38:47.710 --> 38:49.030
I heard you are known as

38:49.030 --> 38:51.230
a very filial son back in your hometown.

38:52.880 --> 38:54.280
The 100,000 you made

38:55.760 --> 38:57.230
from attacking my teacher

38:58.150 --> 38:59.750
was all left to your parents.

39:00.010 --> 39:00.900
So what?

39:03.510 --> 39:04.760
Being filial is good,

39:05.670 --> 39:07.200
but you're just too stupid.

39:09.150 --> 39:10.880
You dropped out of junior high,

39:11.230 --> 39:12.510
so it's understandable

39:12.510 --> 39:13.770
you don't know the law.

39:14.300 --> 39:15.700
But I guarantee you,

39:16.320 --> 39:17.920
your parents won't see a dime

39:18.000 --> 39:19.960
of that 100,000.

39:20.490 --> 39:21.440
What do you mean?

39:24.630 --> 39:25.670
There's no need to get so agitated

39:25.670 --> 39:26.710
about your parents'

39:26.710 --> 39:28.370
miserable life in the future.

39:29.450 --> 39:30.780
You didn't take this job

39:31.290 --> 39:32.680
for them anyway.

39:37.640 --> 39:38.950
Your real purpose

39:39.690 --> 39:41.000
is to go back to prison.

39:43.760 --> 39:45.290
You were jailed for murder.

39:45.880 --> 39:47.510
You were seen as ruthless in jail

39:47.510 --> 39:49.310
and no one dared to mess with you.

39:49.500 --> 39:51.100
But it's different out here.

39:52.190 --> 39:53.790
This is a civilized society.

39:55.190 --> 39:56.750
There's no room for scum.

40:16.640 --> 40:17.410
Hello? Wei?

40:17.760 --> 40:18.590
Jin.

40:18.650 --> 40:20.050
I'm not trying to nag you,

40:20.070 --> 40:21.000
but why didn't you let me know

40:21.000 --> 40:22.320
you're in Jingzhou?

40:22.760 --> 40:23.920
I came in a hurry.

40:24.000 --> 40:24.930
How did you know?

40:25.400 --> 40:28.060
I'm right at the entrance
of the police station.

40:28.650 --> 40:29.980
I passed by after work.

40:30.190 --> 40:31.510
You come out. I won't go in.

40:31.510 --> 40:32.960
Going in means all sorts of small talk.

40:32.960 --> 40:34.220
It's too troublesome.

40:34.400 --> 40:34.960
Okay.

40:34.960 --> 40:35.920
Give me a second.

40:36.760 --> 40:38.360
Is Professor Jiang with you?

40:40.400 --> 40:42.800
It's not very convenient
for him right now.

40:44.230 --> 40:44.940
That's fine.

40:44.940 --> 40:46.140
I just came to see you.

40:46.440 --> 40:46.920
Okay.

40:47.190 --> 40:47.920
Wait for me.

40:47.920 --> 40:48.920
I'll be right out.

40:49.440 --> 40:49.920
Okay.

40:58.760 --> 40:59.400
Wei.

41:02.440 --> 41:02.960
Here.

41:06.800 --> 41:07.660
Fried chicken!

41:07.880 --> 41:08.400
Let's go.

41:08.400 --> 41:09.460
Let's eat by my car.

41:09.480 --> 41:11.070
Where did you park?

41:11.070 --> 41:12.320
Just over there, not far.

41:12.320 --> 41:14.050
There was no place to park here.

41:14.880 --> 41:16.080
There's milk tea too.

41:17.480 --> 41:18.710
Jasmine, 50% sugar.

41:21.550 --> 41:23.350
I haven't had milk tea in so long.

41:26.230 --> 41:26.880
Drink it.

41:26.990 --> 41:27.850
It's still hot.

41:30.920 --> 41:31.480
Drink up.

41:33.800 --> 41:34.510
Let's go.

41:37.190 --> 41:40.120
Director Wang's matter
has spread all over the Provincial Bureau.

41:40.120 --> 41:41.160
How is he doing?

41:41.190 --> 41:43.050
I heard he suffered a head injury.

41:43.710 --> 41:44.840
It's quite serious.

41:45.070 --> 41:47.070
He was in the op room the whole night.

41:47.280 --> 41:48.630
Is he conscious now?

41:53.190 --> 41:54.760
I'm not really sure about that.

41:54.760 --> 41:56.690
Because I haven't seen him either.

41:58.670 --> 42:00.330
What did Professor Jiang say?

42:01.770 --> 42:02.690
About what?

42:04.000 --> 42:07.260
Director Wang's attack
should be related to the 8/17 Case.

42:07.440 --> 42:08.960
Did he find out

42:09.020 --> 42:09.860
any new clues?

42:12.880 --> 42:13.940
He interrogating.

42:14.370 --> 42:16.240
The attacker is tight-lipped.

42:20.000 --> 42:21.110
Still eating?

42:21.510 --> 42:23.550
Aren't you leaving some
for Professor Jiang?

42:23.550 --> 42:24.820
It won't taste good when it's cold.

42:24.820 --> 42:26.820
Besides, he doesn't eat spicy food.

42:36.360 --> 42:36.840
Wei.

42:37.710 --> 42:39.210
I want to ask you something.

42:39.210 --> 42:39.740
Go ahead.

42:41.280 --> 42:42.480
Do you know Zhao Ping?

42:43.000 --> 42:44.150
Zhao Ping?

42:48.190 --> 42:49.630
Not long ago,

42:49.630 --> 42:51.800
we found a problematic colleague
in our team

42:51.800 --> 42:52.730
named Zhao Ping.

42:52.840 --> 42:54.100
How is he problematic?

42:55.480 --> 42:57.320
Passing intel to a criminal gang.

42:57.320 --> 42:58.190
That serious?

42:58.400 --> 43:00.210
He used to be in the SWAT team too.

43:00.400 --> 43:02.200
So I wanted to ask if you know him.

43:02.920 --> 43:03.800
I don't.
